795
00:58:17,369 --> 00:58:18,662
Banyak yang menentang

796
00:58:18,746 --> 00:58:21,582
eksperimen Dokter Choi Dong-eok
di komunitas akademis.

797
00:58:21,665 --> 00:58:23,560
